    <title>服装穿搭</title>
    <link href="/2021/12/13/%E6%9C%8D%E8%A3%85%E7%A9%BF%E6%90%AD/"/>
    <url>/2021/12/13/%E6%9C%8D%E8%A3%85%E7%A9%BF%E6%90%AD/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="衣裤"><a href="#衣裤" class="headerlink" title="衣裤"></a>衣裤</h1><h2 id="夏季"><a href="#夏季" class="headerlink" title="夏季"></a>夏季</h2><h2 id="冬季"><a href="#冬季" class="headerlink" title="冬季"></a>冬季</h2><h3 id="棉衣"><a href="#棉衣" class="headerlink" title="棉衣"></a>棉衣</h3><h3 id="羽绒服"><a href="#羽绒服" class="headerlink" title="羽绒服"></a>羽绒服</h3><ol><li>网易严选羽绒服</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th align="center">尺码</th><th align="center">型号</th><th align="center">肩宽</th><th align="center">胸围</th><th align="center">下摆</th><th align="center">衣长</th><th align="center">袖长</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">L</td><td align="center">175/92A</td><td align="center">47</td><td align="center">116</td><td align="center">104</td><td align="center">67</td><td align="center">64</td></tr></tbody></table><p><img src="./%E6%9C%8D%E8%A3%85%E7%A9%BF%E6%90%AD/%E7%BD%91%E6%98%93%E4%B8%A5%E9%80%89%E7%BE%BD%E7%BB%92%E6%9C%8D.jpg"></p><p>舒适度：L对于我来说偏小，比较适合初冬穿。</p><p>上身效果：上身效果一般，不好穿搭，偏老气。</p><p>经验：不建议以后买修身羽绒服，不好穿搭。</p><p><a href="https://item.jd.com/10035270999569.html#none">商品链接（墨黑）</a></p><h3 id="毛衣"><a href="#毛衣" class="headerlink" title="毛衣"></a>毛衣</h3><ol><li>优衣库毛衣 </li></ol><table><thead><tr><th align="center">尺寸</th><th align="center">后肩衣长</th><th align="center">肩宽</th><th align="center">身宽</th><th align="center">连肩袖长</th><th align="center">领高</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">170/92A(M)</td><td align="center">65</td><td align="center">50.5</td><td align="center">53</td><td align="center">80.5</td><td align="center">5</td></tr></tbody></table><p><img src="./%E6%9C%8D%E8%A3%85%E7%A9%BF%E6%90%AD/%E4%BC%98%E8%A1%A3%E5%BA%93%E6%AF%9B%E8%A1%A31.jpg"><br><img src="./%E6%9C%8D%E8%A3%85%E7%A9%BF%E6%90%AD/%E4%BC%98%E8%A1%A3%E5%BA%93%E6%AF%9B%E8%A1%A32.jpg"></p><p>舒适度：很舒服。</p><p>上身效果：衣服略大，略长。</p><p><a href="https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?id=653336177825&spm=a1z09.2.0.0.c6b22e8dgkmhFK&_u=i34fo86laf7e">商品链接（乳白色）</a></p><h3 id="卫裤"><a href="#卫裤" class="headerlink" title="卫裤"></a>卫裤</h3><ol><li>二十八间卫裤</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th align="center">规格</th><th align="center">裤长</th><th align="center">腰围</th><th align="center">臀围</th><th align="center">脚口</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">L</td><td align="center">97</td><td align="center">72-92</td><td align="center">120</td><td align="center">束脚</td></tr></tbody></table><p><img src="./%E6%9C%8D%E8%A3%85%E7%A9%BF%E6%90%AD/%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E9%97%B4%E5%8D%AB%E8%A3%A41.jpg"><br><img src="./%E6%9C%8D%E8%A3%85%E7%A9%BF%E6%90%AD/%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E9%97%B4%E5%8D%AB%E8%A3%A42.jpg"></p><p>舒适度：很舒服。</p><p>上身效果：胯部偏低。</p><p><a href="https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z09.2.0.0.4f3e2e8dYYcndC&id=649344880656&_u=j34fo86l9430">商品链接（灰色加绒款）</a></p><h3 id="直筒裤"><a href="#直筒裤" class="headerlink" title="直筒裤"></a>直筒裤</h3><h1 id="鞋"><a href="#鞋" class="headerlink" title="鞋"></a>鞋</h1><h3 id="休闲鞋"><a href="#休闲鞋" class="headerlink" title="休闲鞋"></a>休闲鞋</h3><h3 id="帆布鞋"><a href="#帆布鞋" class="headerlink" title="帆布鞋"></a>帆布鞋</h3><h3 id="马丁靴"><a href="#马丁靴" class="headerlink" title="马丁靴"></a>马丁靴</h3><h1 id="配饰"><a href="#配饰" class="headerlink" title="配饰"></a>配饰</h1>]]></content>
    
    
